longBusinessSummary: Idle Media Inc. operates as an online media and entertainment company. It primarily owns and operates DatPiff, the source for new music and the collection of mixtapes on the Web. The company is based in Leesport, Pennsylvania. Idle Media, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Zoeter, LLC.
